343
00:21:51,603 --> 00:21:54,147
<i>Delusion of being deceived
perpetually drooling</i>

344
00:21:54,231 --> 00:21:56,775
<i>Judgement is "crime control"
they drive/ed</i>

345
00:21:56,942 --> 00:21:59,444
<i>Who has the Rx for that?</i>

346
00:21:59,528 --> 00:22:02,113
<i>A decriminalized world</i>

347
